{"tid":2008924,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[支持Rthk] 立法會下週一討論港台管治，一人一信撐RTHK！","createTime":"2020-05-09T11:21:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-11T11:08:50.000Z","uid":41818,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"242197e21ad5db7e6f8d6ab2b6da51d34dc6054a","tid":2008924,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T11:21:00.000Z","msg":"Forward, from 一群香港電台節目顧問團成員：<br />\n<br />\n8 May 2020 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n立法會資訊科技及廣播事務委員會將於下星期一（5月11日）下午討論議程 【香港電台的管治及管理】，可以預計香港電台將面對政府和保皇黨夾攻，需要香港人出聲撐！(商經局就香港電台的管治及管理提供的文件)<br />\n<br />\n希望大家寫信去立法會資訊科技及廣播事務委員會表達你對香港電台的支持，要求政府停止政治干預，讓港台維持編輯自主和言論自由，而不是言論審查，要港台變成官方喉舌！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">電郵地址： panel_itb@legco.gov.hk\n\n電郵標題：一名香港市民就5月11日議程【香港電台的管治及管理】之意見</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n引申：<br />\n梁家榮「港台面向社會變風眼」 籲員工守約章　勿違一國原則<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200507/MPDPL6IPTUG4IZOPPQYEGIY2GQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200507%2FMPDPL6IPTUG4IZOPPQYEGIY2GQ%2F&d=i%2FQ10njZfEvfzeNkfPb7d83u7Zzj2Sx3DhCMrptFZ9w%3D&h=f937ddcf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200507%2FMPDPL6IPTUG4IZOPPQYEGIY2GQ%2F&h=be11b2d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200507/MPDPL6IPTUG4IZOPPQYEGIY2GQ/</a>"},{"pid":"9fe004535dfc7e7e6eb963ad88278cee4f5eb5d2","tid":2008924,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T11:22:43.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/4nzUThz8BvI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F4nzUThz8BvI&d=i%2FQ10njZfEvfzeNkfPb7d83u7Zzj2Sx3DhCMrptFZ9w%3D&h=8456846d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/4nzUThz8BvI</a>"},{"pid":"91d66d7ff0e24e5d9277c8ddb725448d6f3d5032","tid":2008924,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9fe004535dfc7e7e6eb963ad88278cee4f5eb5d2","tid":2008924,"uid":48